\alpha(\theta_{i} + \theta_{j})=(\theta_{i} + \theta_{j})(1)=\theta_{i}(1) + \theta_{j}(1)=\alpha(\theta_{i})+\alpha(\theta_{j})
\alpha(\theta_{i}\theta_{j})=\theta_{i}(\theta_{j}(1))=\theta_{i}(j)=ij=\alpha(\theta_{i})\alpha(\theta_{j})
\alpha(\theta_{i})=\alpha(\theta_{j})
\theta_{i}(1)=\theta_{j}(1)
\theta_{i}=\theta_{j}
